    rating: "Great"
    comments: "The concept is great as the story of Daniel Plainview is an allegory on the rise of capitalism at the turn of the century; the plot structure is laid out very well; the character writing is incredible as Daniel Plainview iconically portays the greed of men and the lengths they will go to appease it"
  }
