      name: "Paul Thomas Anderson"
    }
    rating: "Great"
    comments: "The dialogue is well crafted and filled with iconic lines that highlight who Daniel Plainview is; the symbolism is incredibly profound as the movie touches on the rise of capitalism at the turn of the century and the conflict between greed and religion; the foreshadowing is great as film really comes full circle as PTA plants seeds that grow and come out in the end"
  }
